<TITLE>Seeking Native American Spirituality and Traditional Religion: Read This First!</TITLE>

<META NAME="description" CONTENT="A word to the wise for non-Indians in search of Native American religions and spirituality. Explains the differences
between traditional American Indian belief and European paganism, Russian shamanism, and the New Age.">
<meta charset="utf-8"/> 				

</HEAD>

